snippet.textDisplay:
Coke Studio Bangla:
1. Nasek Nasek: Tribal language+ folk song. released on int. mother language day.
2. Prarthona: Means prayer, traditional prayer song of farmers mainly+ sufi spritual song. released on 1st ramadan.
3. Bulbuli: Gazal by our Natiaonal poet+ classical modern song with tango music (both about spring vibes). released on 1st day of Bangla new year.
4. Bhober pagol: Sufi lalon folk song fused rock version+ rap+ groovy vibe (both about inner mistry of the world, about how crazy everything n everyone from within). released on Eid day.
